e="contact_customer_care">CUSTOMER CARE</string><string name="contact_title">CONTACT TIREDCITY</string><string name="contact_subtitle">Leave a message, the TiredCity team will respond as soon as possible to support you.</string><string name="hint_name">Full Name *</string><string name="hint_phone_contact">Phone Number *</string><string name="hint_message_long">Your message *</string><string name="btn_send_message">SEND MESSAGE ✦</string><string name="title_store_locator">STORE LOCATOR</string><string name="label_address">Address: </string><string name="label_opening_hours">Opening hours: </string><string name="label_email">Email: </string><string name="label_mobile">Mobile: </string><string name="link_view_map">View map</string><string name="map_tap_hint">Tap to view all locations on Google Maps</string><string name="store_1_name">1. TiredCity 37 Hàng Hành</string><string name="store_1_details">Address: 37 P. Hàng Hành, Hàng Trống, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội. View map\nOpening hours: 9:00 - 22:30 (Mon - Sun)\nEmail: hello@tiredcity.com\nMobile: 024 6296 0306</string><string name="store_2_name">2. TiredCity 97 Hàng Gai</string><string name="store_2_details">Address: 97 P. Hàng Gai, Hàng Trống, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội. View map\nOpening hours: 9:00 - 22:30 (Mon - Sun)\nEmail: hello@tiredcity.com\nMobile: 024 6296 0306</string><string name="store_3_name">3. TiredCity 19 Nhà Thờ</string><string name="store_3_details">Address: 19 P. Nhà Thờ, Hàng Trống, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội. View map\nOpening hours: 9:00 - 22:30 (Mon - Sun)\nEmail: hello@tiredcity.com\nMobile: 024 6296 0306</string><string name="store_4_name">4. TiredCity 100 Hàng Đào</string><string name="store_4_details">Address: 100 P. Hàng Đào, Hàng Đào, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội. View map\nOpening hours: 9:00 - 22:30 (Mon - Sun)\nEmail: hello@tiredcity.com\nMobile: 024 6296 0306</string><string name="store_5_name">5. TiredCity 8 Lương Ngọc Quyến</string><string name="store_5_details">Address: 8 P. Lương Ngọc Quyến, Hàng Buồm, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội. View map\nOpening hours: 9:00 - 22:30 (Mon - Sun)\nEmail: hello@tiredcity.com\nMobile: 024 6296 0306</string><string name="policy_subtitle">Learn about TiredCity\'s policies and terms to ensure a safe and meaningful shopping experience.</string><string name="policy_purchase_title">Purchase Policy</string><string name="policy_purchase_content"><![CDATA[
        <b>Order Confirmation Time</b><br/>
        After a customer successfully places an order, we will contact you for confirmation within 24 business hours.<br/><br/>
        <b>Order Conditions</b><br/>
        • Customers must provide complete delivery information.<br/>
        • Phone number and address information must be accurate.<br/>
        • Orders must be confirmed before delivery proceeds.<br/><br/>
        <b>Purchase Process</b><br/>
        1. Select the desired product.<br/>
        2. Add the product to the cart.<br/>
        3. Fill in the delivery information.<br/>
        4. Choose a payment method.<br/>
        5. Confirm the order.<br/>
        6. Receive a confirmation notice from the store.<br/><br/>
        <b>Note</b><br/>
        The store reserves the right to refuse orders with signs of fraud or inaccurate information.
    ]]></string><string name="policy_payment_title">Payment Policy</string><string name="policy_payment_content"><![CDATA[
        <b>Payment Methods</b><br/>
        • Cash on Delivery (COD).<br/>
        • Bank transfer.<br/>
        • E-wallets (MoMo, ZaloPay, VNPay…).<br/>
        • Credit/Debit cards.<br/><br/>
        <b>Payment Security</b><br/>
        • All online transactions are encrypted and secured.<br/>
        • Customer payment information is not stored without authorization.<br/>
        • Used payment gateways all meet safety standards.<br/><br/>
        <b>Refund Policy</b><br/>
        • Refunds will be processed after the return request is confirmed.<br/>
        • Refund processing time is from 05 – 07 business days.<br/><br/>
        <b>Note</b><br/>
        Customers should keep transaction information for verification if needed.
    ]]></string><string name="policy_shipping_title">Shipping Policy</string><string name="policy_shipping_content"><![CDATA[
        <b>Delivery Time</b><br/>
        • Inner City: 01 – 03 business days.<br/>
        • Suburbs and other provinces: 03 – 07 business days.<br/><br/>
        <b>Shipping Range</b><br/>
        We support nationwide delivery through reputable shipping units.<br/><br/>
        <b>Shipping Process</b><br/>
        1. Order is confirmed.<br/>
        2. Products are packaged and handed over to the shipping unit.<br/>
        3. Customer receives order tracking information.<br/>
        4. Delivery to the registered address.<br/><br/>
        <b>Note</b><br/>
        Delivery time may vary due to weather, holidays, or other objective factors.
    ]]></string><string name="policy_return_title">Return And Refund Policy</string><string name="policy_return_content"><![CDATA[
        <b>Return Period</b><br/>
        We accept returns within 07 days from the date the customer receives the product.<br/><br/>
        <b>Product Return Conditions</b><br/>
        • Product is in original condition with tags attached.<br/>
        • Unused and unwashed.<br/>
        • Not damaged by the customer.<br/>
        • Have an invoice or proof of purchase.<br/><br/>
        <b>Return Process</b><br/>
        1. Contact the customer care department.<br/>
        2. Provide images or videos of the product.<br/>
        3. Pack and send the product to the store.<br/>
        4. Receive a new product or a refund as regulated.<br/><br/>
        <b>Note</b><br/>
        Shipping costs incurred during the return process will be handled on a case-by-case basis.
    ]]></string><string name="policy_privacy_title">Privacy Policy</string><string name="policy_privacy_content"><![CDATA[
        <b>Purpose of Information Collection</b><br/>
        • Process orders.<br/>
        • Support customer care.<br/>
        • Improve service quality.<br/>
        • Send promotional information (if the customer agrees).<br/><br/>
        <b>Scope of Information Use</b><br/>
        • Used only for activities related to providing products and services.<br/>
        • Do not share with third parties without customer consent, except as required by law.<br/><br/>
        <b>Data Security</b><br/>
        • Personal information is stored on a secure system.<br/>
        • Apply technical measures to prevent unauthorized access.<br/>
        • Regularly check and upgrade the security system.<br/><br/>
        <b>Customer Rights</b><br/>
        • Request correction or update of personal information.<br/>
        • Request to stop receiving advertising information.<br/>
        • Request deletion of personal data according to current regulations.
    ]]></string><string name="str_policy_term">POLICY &amp; TERMS</string></file><file path="D:\TiredCity-App\app\src\main\res\values\themes.xml" qualifiers=""><style name="Theme.TiredCity" parent="Theme.Material3.Light.NoActionBar">
